urls.title: Trip Report - The 2022 Arctic Cowboys Northwest Passage Kayak Expedition - The Arctic Cowboys
urls.description: Our goal, since the idea came across my mind back in 2019, was to be the first team to kayak the entire 2000+ miles of the infamous Northwest Passage, which wound its way through the Canadian Arctic Archipelago, through a variety of routes, from Baffin Bay to the Beaufort Sea.
